{"tid":2320537,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美聯邦通訊委員會確認華為威脅國家安全","createTime":"2020-12-11T01:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T07:18:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7574ada7d7fe00f5b7cf1952a3ad33750de913","tid":2320537,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"美聯邦通訊委員會確認華為威脅國家安全<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國聯邦通訊委員會正式確認，中國電訊設備商華為對美國國家安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦通訊委員會今年六月將華為及中興通訊，列入對國家安全構成威脅的名單之中，禁止美國公司動用83億美元政府資金，向相關公司購買電訊設備，華為其後提出申訴，要求重新考慮將華為從名單中剔除。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦通訊委員會周四正式拒絕華為的申請，認為華為確實威脅美國的國家安全，而通訊委員會在上月已經正式確認，將中興通訊維持列入國安威脅名單之中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416171&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2Wrppvqc%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=ba043664\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416171&h=3d795c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416171</a>"},{"pid":"9e56bbb7e9962c9fa5a247b64218ade4f26e7bec","tid":2320537,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"國家安全好重要架<br />\n全面封鎖佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd0be8dc84985a24f05655e6d0563c214e65c7a","tid":2320537,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0408da25a1c88ab66ec0c42d78862fd96731164e","tid":2320537,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"拜登上台立即取消<br />\n仲要馬上歡迎華為"},{"pid":"6c1cc55dcb8908ffe721ba2bf680164670d28c13","tid":2320537,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\